data.name: grdOCS2016.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.PKOCS2016 , A.FKOCS2015 , A.SEQ , A.HANGMOG_CODE , B.HANGMOG_NAME , A.SURYANG , A.NALSU , A.ORD_DANUI , A.BOGYONG_CODE , A.JUSA_CODE , A.JUSA_SPD_GUBUN , A.DV , A.DV_TIME , A.FKOCS2003 FROM OCS2016 A , OCS0103 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.FKOCS2015 = :f_fkocs2015 AND A.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND A.HANGMOG_CODE = B.HANGMOG_CODE

data.name: grdOCS2015.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.PKOCS2015 , A.BUNHO , A.FKINP1001 , A.ORDER_DATE , A.INPUT_GUBUN , A.PK_SEQ , A.SEQ , A.ACT_DATE , A.ACT_ID , A.ACT_RESULT_CODE, A.ACT_RESULT_TEXT, A.INPUT_ID FROM OCS2015 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.FKINP1001 = :f_fkinp1001 AND A.ORDER_DATE = :f_order_date AND A.INPUT_GUBUN = :f_input_gubun AND A.PK_SEQ = :f_pk_seq AND A.ACT_DATE = :f_act_date

data.name: grdOCS2006.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT '' AS CHK , A.FKOCS2005 , A.HANGMOG_CODE , B.HANGMOG_NAME , A.SURYANG , A.ORD_DANUI , A.DV , A.DV_TIME , A.NALSU , A.BOGYONG_CODE , A.JUSA_CODE , A.JUSA_SPD_GUBUN , A.BUNHO , A.FKINP1001 , A.ORDER_DATE , A.INPUT_GUBUN , A.PK_SEQ , A.SEQ , A.DIRECT_GUBUN , A.DIRECT_CODE , A.DIRECT_DETAIL , C.CODE_NAME AS JUSA_CODE_NAME, D.CODE_NAME AS JUSA_SPD_NAME, NVL(E.BOGYONG_NAME, A.BOGYONG_CODE) AS BOGYONG_NAME FROM OCS2006 A , OCS0103 B , OCS0132 C , OCS0132 D , DRG0120 E WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.FKOCS2005 = :f_fkocs2005 AND A.PK_SEQ = :f_pk_seq AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.CODE_TYPE(+) = 'JUSA' AND C.CODE(+) = A.JUSA_CODE AND D.HOSP_CODE(+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.CODE_TYPE(+) = 'JUSA_SPD_GUBUN' AND D.CODE(+) = A.JUSA_SPD_GUBUN AND E.HOSP_CODE (+) = A.HOSP_CODE AND E.BOGYONG_CODE(+)= A.BOGYONG_CODE

data.name: grdNUR0114.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT '' AS CHK, A.NUR_ACT_CODE , A.NUR_ACT_NAME FROM NUR0113 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.NUR_GR_CODE = :f_direct_gubun AND A.NUR_MD_CODE = :f_direct_code -- AND A.NUR_SO_CODE = :f_direct_detail AND A.VALD = 'Y' ORDER BY A.SORT_KEY
